      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 40:12",
      "source_id": "kjv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-kjv2006/PSA040.htm",
      "text": "For innumerable evils have compassed me about: mine iniquities have taken hold upon me, so that I am not able to look up; they are more than the hairs of mine head: therefore my heart faileth me.",
      "versionTitle": "King James Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 40:12",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA040.htm",
      "text": "For innumerable evils have compassed me about; Mine iniquities have overtaken me, so that I am not able to look up; They are more than the hairs of my head; And my heart hath failed me.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
